title: Coincidence

description.plain: Seemingly inspired by country and folk songs of the seventies, especially Joni Mitchell’s “Big Yellow Taxi”, “Coincidence” sees a continuation of the love betrayal from “Sharpest Tool” in the narrative. Carpenter mocks her ex-partner for playing her around when it comes to the relationship, making fun of his bad excuses and cheekily jabbing him by saying it’s just a ‘coincidence’ how he ends up with other girls.
